{"tid":2168730,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"(地獄鬼國之日常) 有片 大陸佬將自己2歲既BB掟死左！","createTime":"2020-08-22T03:28:55.000Z","updateTime":"2020-08-23T05:38:40.000Z","uid":222970,"like":118,"dislike":6,"uniUserReply":95,"replies":[{"pid":"e5413e25d770edbf5659bbd8eb555e95a409c30a","tid":2168730,"uid":222970,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-22T03:28:55.000Z","msg":"有片<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/100049495734310/posts/165242895135567/?extid=kP4rlnJBkEYbsmGf&amp;d=n\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2F100049495734310%2Fposts%2F165242895135567%2F%3Fextid%3DkP4rlnJBkEYbsmGf%26d%3Dn&d=4FeJsexKtrFIFozdf5QThgOzzNjRw9ZJ5YgnvwIkb18%3D&h=04d0855c\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/100049495734310/posts/165242895135567/?extid=kP4rlnJBkEYbsmGf&amp;d=n</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/BB4jS5m.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FBB4jS5m.gif&h=9955ec57&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n【#陝西遭父親抱摔幼童死亡#】8月20日，一段男子抱摔幼童的視頻在網絡上瘋傳，這段僅僅7秒的視頻引起熱議。視頻顯示，一名男子兩次用力把兩三歲的幼童舉起後重重摔向沙發，孩子從沙發滾至地上，大聲啼哭。警方通報，經調査，犯罪嫌疑人劉某酒後與女友馮某因兩人所生小孩（兩歲六個月）撫養問題發生爭執，將小孩拋摔在沙發上，致小孩受傷。目前犯罪嫌疑人劉某已被刑事拘留，案件正在辦理。不幸的是，據多方證實，昨晚孩子經搶救無效死亡。陝西寶雞2歲半幼童遭父親抱摔：經搶救無效死亡<br />\n<br />\n據一位不便透露姓名的知情人士說：「接診後，孩子先進行了心肺復蘇，經診斷為閉合性顱腦損傷、廣泛腦水腫、繼發性腦幹損傷等，目前在重症監護室接受進一步的治療。」<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://m.weibo.cn/search?containerid=231522type%3D1%26t%3D10%26q%3D%23陕西遭父亲抱摔幼童死亡%23&amp;extparam=%23陕西遭父亲抱摔幼童死亡%23&amp;luicode=10000011&amp;lfid=231522&amp;featurecode=newtitle%20我的手机%202019%2F1%2F29%2020%3A39%3A19\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fm.weibo.cn%2Fsearch%3Fcontainerid%3D231522type%253D1%2526t%253D10%2526q%253D%2523%E9%99%95%E8%A5%BF%E9%81%AD%E7%88%B6%E4%BA%B2%E6%8A%B1%E6%91%94%E5%B9%BC%E7%AB%A5%E6%AD%BB%E4%BA%A1%2523%26extparam%3D%2523%E9%99%95%E8%A5%BF%E9%81%AD%E7%88%B6%E4%BA%B2%E6%8A%B1%E6%91%94%E5%B9%BC%E7%AB%A5%E6%AD%BB%E4%BA%A1%2523%26luicode%3D10000011%26lfid%